Big Brother Naija, BBNaija housemate, Lilo has spoken on her relationship with Eric in the house. Lilo was evicted alongside Ka3na during Sunday’s live eviction show. They were among four housemates alongside Praise and Eric with the least votes. Speaking on her relationship with Eric, Lilo said she still feels the same about him. She, however, did not give more details on situation with her boyfriend outside the house. On her eviction from the show, Lilo said she was surprised. She told Ebuka: “I thought I was going to be in the house longer. “I’m surprised at the eviction but I don’t know why they did not save me.” On her next step outside the house, Lilo said she would go for her Masters Degree and focus on her business too.